name: Gradient Rock Necklace
description:
Our newest edition to the rock collection features a large faceted sandstone rock with a gradient! 

Each piece is unique and 'cut' from a larger set of rocks. The color is printed directly into the material during the 3d printing process. 

Color and shape will vary.

24" sterling silver chain. No clasp.

name: Drawings - Group A
description:
Utilizing the same custom algorithms used to generate our 3d faceted rock shapes, each image is individually produced as 2d vectors, then drawn mechanically using a CNC machine that methodically draws the line work with a pen. Multiple passes add line weight and selective color.
